    "description": "本課程除了課本之外，會提供線上學習教材。<br>全球英語(一): 著重於培養學生勇於開口說英語的膽量和意願。以情境和角色扮演的上課模式鼓勵學生群組練習開口說英語。透過口語反覆練習讓學生熟習單字和文法，以取代傳統的背誦和死記學習模式。<br>The objective of Globish (一) is to encourage students to speak English with real-word activities, rather than the monotonous recitation learning mode. With the designed scenarios, students will improve English-speaking ability, and furthermore remember the words and the structure of sentences.",
